Read more about survival analysis

Overview

Learn more about how it's calculated?
  • Active contributors ?
    × Contributors who have made at least one contribution to a project or community in the past year.
  • Newcomers ?
    × Contributors who have made their inaugural contribution within the last 60 days.
  • Contributors left ?
    × Contributors who, having previously contributed, have been inactive or not contributed to the project for over a year.
  • Average tenure (days) ?
    × Mean duration contributors have been actively engaged with the project.
  • % Turnover rate ?
    × Percentage of contributors who have left the project relative to the total number of contributors.
  • Total contributors ?
    × Cumulative number of contributors within the selected time frame.
